<en-note><span STYLE="border-collapse: separate; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.300781); -webkit-composition-fill-color: rgba(175, 192, 227, 0.234375); -webkit-composition-frame-color: rgba(77, 128, 180, 0.234375); -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-size: medium; "><span STYLE="border-collapse: collapse; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Tahoma, 'Microsoft Yahei', Simsun; font-size: 15px; line-height: 30px; ">
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="word-wrap: break-word; " ALIGN="center"><font STYLE="word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; "><br STYLE="word-wrap: break-word; "/>&nbsp; &nbsp; 很多准备移民英国的客户，会质疑中国的手机带到英国，是否可以继续使用。答案是：可以，只需要购买一张不签约的sim卡，也就是pay as you go 手机卡就可以了。</font></div>
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="word-wrap: break-word; " ALIGN="left"></div>
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="word-wrap: break-word; " ALIGN="left"><font STYLE="word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; ">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 英国各大手机运营公司，如沃达丰，O2，Orange等都有这样的 Pay as you go 手机卡。在各家店铺可以买得到，既不需要你提供任何个人信息也不需要和银行卡绑定。但各家公司的信号，资费都不同，需依据个人情况选择。</font></div>
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="word-wrap: break-word; " ALIGN="left"></div>
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="word-wrap: break-word; " ALIGN="left"><font STYLE="word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; ">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; Pay as you go 手机卡的好处就是用户可以想什么时候用就什么时候充值，不用就扔在一边。想更换手机号码也挺简单，把手中这样pay as you go 手机卡停用，重买一张新的手机卡就可以了。</font></div>
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="word-wrap: break-word; " ALIGN="left"></div>
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;
&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="word-wrap: break-word; " ALIGN="left"><font STYLE="word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; ">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 总的来说，个人pay as you go是比较灵活方便的，对于每月通话不是特别多，特别固定的人来讲，是一个不错的选择。初到英国可以考虑pay as you go手机卡，因为刚到英国，能尽快有一个可以让人联系的电话号码还是很重要的。</font></div>
&Tab;&Tab;
